      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of atmospheric engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, this specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe, rod bearing replacement, and a complete VANOS overhaul. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, delivering power through a perfectly dialed M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains incredibly rigid, supported by a factory-spec suspension that retains original damping characteristics. Finished in collector-grade condition with immaculate paint depth and a pristine interior, this is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle optimized for both mechanical longevity and peak lateral acceleration.",
